‚ÄúSettlement Method‚Äù --> how the trade is finished at the end
CASH settlement ((Money only)) ->
You bet on NIFTY index:
                      You cannot buy NIFTY
                      You only get profit / loss money
In T24 terms
No share / no bond / no commodity
Only accounting entries

 What you SEE in T24

‚úÖ DX Trade ‚Üí CLOSED
‚úÖ Accounting entry
‚ùå NO SEC.TRADE

Typical instruments = CASH
Equity Index
FX Cash
Volatility
OFU (Future into cash)

PHYSICAL settlement (Asset + money) -> 
You buy TCS share option:
                       If exercised ‚Üí you receive shares
                       You also pay money

In T24 terms
Security must be delivered
New SEC.TRADE is created
Then trade closes

What you SEE in T24

‚úÖ DX Trade ‚Üí CLOSED
‚úÖ SEC.TRADE created
‚úÖ SEC.TRADE status = IHLD / AUTH
‚úÖ Accounting entries




Contract Type
   |
   |-- OPTION ---------------------+
   |                               |
   |                         Premium Style
   |                               |
   |             OPTION_STYLE      FUTURE_STYLE
   |             (pay premium)     (margin-based)
   |
   |-- FUTURE ------------------ FUTURE_STYLE only


Example: Gold price = $2,000 per ounce 
OPTION √ó OPTION_STYLE
‚ÄúPay now, decide later.‚Äù
Real life
You pay $100 today to get the right to buy gold at $2,000 after 1 month.
If gold ‚Üí $2,200 ‚Üí you exercise
If gold ‚Üí $1,800 ‚Üí you walk away
Your maximum loss = $100


Contract Type  : OPTION
Premium Style  : OPTION_STYLE
Option Type    : CALL
Strike Price   : 2000
Premium        : 100 (paid today)

 OPTION √ó FUTURE_STYLE
‚ÄúNo premium today, settle later‚Äù ‚Üê üî• IMPORTANT
Real life

You do not pay $100 today.

Instead:
You agree on $2,000
Profit/Loss is settled later
You still have a right, not obligation

You MUST still agree on:
BUY or SELL
PRICE
Otherwise the contract is meaningless.

Contract Type  : OPTION
Premium Style  : FUTURE_STYLE
Option Type    : CALL
Strike Price   : 2000
Premium        : NONE upfront
Settlement     : At maturity


FUTURE √ó FUTURE_STYLE
‚ÄúNo choice, compulsory trade‚Äù
Real life
You must buy gold at $2,000 after 1 month.
No right to walk away
No premium
Both sides obligated

Contract Type  : FUTURE
Premium Style  : FUTURE_STYLE
Option Type    : ‚ùå
Strike Price   : ‚ùå





